                "invention-title": [
                    "Small-scale transformation method and system for adjusting hydrogen-carbon balance",
                    "一种调节氢碳平衡的小比例变换方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a small-proportion shift method and system for adjusting hydrogen-carbon balance, and solves the problem of carbon-hydrogen complementary balance of coal synthesis gas and oilfield synthesis gas, the method comprises the following steps: step 1, coal crude synthesis gas produced by raw material coal enters a gas-liquid separator to separate water, and then becomes dry synthesis gas; step 2, the dry synthesis gas is divided into two streams, one stream of dry mixed gas is subjected to CO conversion hydrogen production reaction to generate converted gas, the converted gas and the other stream of dry mixed gas are mixed to form converted mixed gas, and the converted mixed gas is cooled by a cooling device to form low-temperature coal synthesis gas; and 3, mixing the oilfield synthesis gas with the low-temperature coal synthesis gas to obtain methanol synthesis gas, and adjusting the gas volume ratio of the two dry mixed gases to ensure the hydrogen-carbon balance of the coal synthesis gas and the oilfield synthesis gas. The system is based on the method, one strand of dry mixed gas is used for generating H2 through the CO conversion hydrogen production reaction, the H2 content is increased, the CO content is reduced, and the hydrogen-carbon balance of the converted mixed gas is effectively achieved by controlling the gas amount when the two strands of dry mixed gas are shunted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种调节氢碳平衡的小比例变换方法及系统，解决煤制合成气和油田制合成气的碳氢互补平衡问题，方法包括：步骤一、原料煤生产的煤制粗合成气进入气液分离器分离水之后变成干合成气；步骤二、干合成气分成两股，一股干混合气发生CO变换制氢反应生成变换气，变换气与另一股干混合气混合成变换混合气，变换混合气经过降温装置降温成低温煤制合成气；步骤三、将油田制合成气与低温煤制合成气混合成甲醇合成气，调节两股干混合气的气量比，确保煤制合成气与油田制合成气的氢碳平衡。系统基于上述方法，本发明采用CO变换制氢反应将一股干混合气生成H2，增加了H2含量、降低了CO含量，控制两股干混合气分流时的气体量有效实现变换混合气的氢碳平衡。"
                }
            ]
